<promed@promedmail.org>
[Paradoxically poultry industry workers and poultry cullers in
Southeast Asia have rarely,if ever, exhibited over signs and symptoms
oft avian influenza virus infection; human disease being associated
mainly with domestic situations and food preparation. - mod.CP]
